    <h3>9.	Prisoner’s Dilemma Summary</h3>

    The prisoner’s dilemma paradox is still a topic of study today because it extends far beyond the basic scenarios introduced in this learning module. It can teach us about human behaviour in conflict, competition between rival businesses, diplomacy between countries during war, and much more.

